(83, 4, 'What is the maturity time for this investment?', 'The maturity time for this investment is 18 months, but returns will continue beyond this period as long as the livestock farming project remains operational.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:52:44', '2024-10-01 03:52:44'),
(84, 4, 'How does the project ensure sustainability in livestock farming?', 'The project follows sustainable livestock practices such as rotational grazing, organic feed, and reduced use of antibiotics. These methods ensure long-term sustainability and environmental protection.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:52:44', '2024-10-01 03:52:44'),
(85, 4, 'What is the minimum investment amount?', 'The minimum investment is determined by the share price, which is based on the project\'s overall goal and the number of available shares. Investors can participate by purchasing one or more shares.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:52:44', '2024-10-01 03:52:44'),
(86, 3, 'What are the benefits of investing in Organic Vegetable Farming?', 'Investing in Organic Vegetable Farming supports eco-friendly agriculture that avoids the use of synthetic chemicals. This project promotes soil health, environmental protection, and stable returns due to the growing demand for organic produce.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:35', '2024-10-01 03:53:35'),
(87, 3, 'How are the returns calculated for Organic Vegetable Farming?', 'Returns are calculated based on the production and sale of organic vegetables, with investors receiving consistent returns as long as the project remains operational.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:35', '2024-10-01 03:53:35'),
(88, 3, 'What is the maturity time for this investment?', 'The maturity time for this investment is 16 months, but returns will continue beyond this period as long as the organic farming project is operational.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:35', '2024-10-01 03:53:35'),
(89, 3, 'How does the project ensure sustainability in organic farming?', 'The project uses organic farming techniques that focus on crop rotation, natural pest control, and composting. These methods ensure long-term sustainability and the production of healthy, chemical-free vegetables.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:35', '2024-10-01 03:53:35'),
(90, 3, 'What is the minimum investment amount?', 'The minimum investment is based on the project\'s share price, which is determined by its total goal and available shares. Investors can participate by purchasing one or more shares.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:35', '2024-10-01 03:53:35'),
(91, 2, 'What are the benefits of investing in Sustainable Corn Farming?', 'Investing in Sustainable Corn Farming supports environmentally friendly practices that promote soil health and water conservation. Corn is a high-demand crop, ensuring stable returns for investors.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:58', '2024-10-01 03:53:58'),
