(94, 2, 'How does the project ensure sustainability in corn farming?', 'The project implements sustainable farming practices, including crop rotation, organic fertilization, and water conservation. These methods ensure the long-term viability of corn farming and environmental protection.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:53:58', '2024-10-01 03:53:58'),
