(96, 1, 'What are the benefits of investing in Sustainable Rice Farming?', 'Investing in Sustainable Rice Farming supports eco-friendly farming practices that reduce water usage and promote soil health. Rice is a staple crop globally, ensuring long-term demand and stable returns.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:58:38', '2024-10-01 03:58:38'),
(97, 1, 'How are the returns calculated for Sustainable Rice Farming?', 'Returns are based on regular harvest cycles, with investors benefiting from the consistent demand for rice. The project ensures profitability through efficient and sustainable farming methods.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:58:38', '2024-10-01 03:58:38'),
(98, 1, 'What is the maturity time for this investment?', 'The maturity time for this investment is 12 months, but returns will continue beyond this period as long as the rice farming project remains operational.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:58:38', '2024-10-01 03:58:38'),
(99, 1, 'How does the project ensure sustainability in rice farming?', 'The project uses sustainable rice farming practices such as water-efficient irrigation, organic fertilizers, and crop rotation. These methods ensure long-term sustainability and environmental resilience.', 1, '2024-10-01 03:58:38', '2024-10-01 03:58:38'),
